@startuml
!theme plain
title 11. KV Durability Classes
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "KV object" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "KV-D0..KV-D5 policy" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Coherence placement" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "OpenZFS persistence" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Recovery semantics" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : classify
N2 --> N3 : retention goal
N3 --> N4 : memory/storage target
N4 --> N5 : durability evidence

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
